    "width": 306,
    "z": 185,
    "movable": false,
    "text": "Look at the meeple and stick below in the JSON editor and note the `resetProperties`. The grey pawn and house also have resetProperties. The button above updates the properties on the widget to match the `resetProperties`. So they will move, rotate, and scale as needed. A css transition is applied to the widgets to clearly demonstrate the effect."
